<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV8">
<l>kāṇkiṉṟa ṉakaḷuṅ kēṭkiṉ ṟaṉakaḷuṅ kāṇilinnāḷ</l>
<l>pāṇkuṉṟa nāṭar payilkiṉ ṟaṉavitel lāmaṟintō</l>
<l>māṇkuṉṟa mēntittaṇ māmalai vēṅkaṭat tumparnampuñ</l>
<l>cēṇkuṉṟañ ceṉṟu poruḷpaṭaip pāṉkaṟṟa tiṇṇaṉavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When we see what is seen and what is heard these days</l>
<l>we understand all this, the things practised by men from the land of lauded hills:</l>
<l>the certainties learned by the one who creates wealth , going to distant hills,</l>
<l>who longs beyond for Vēṅkaṭam, cool dark mountain of the glorious hill’s lifter.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
